Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.44,Main,L,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.26,Main,T,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.38,Main,T,0,0,0,,我还没有赢过你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.42,Main,Fafnir,0,0,0,,今天要来试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.02,Main,L,0,0,0,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.54,Main,K,0,0,0,,咦 是不是不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:21.98,Main,Kanna,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.26,Italics,K,0,0,0,,这之后…
