Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:39.52,Main,Kanna,0,0,0,,哦 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.00,Main,Saikawa,0,0,0,,喂 康娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.98,Main,Kanna,0,0,0,,才川不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.90,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,好了 开始上课
